      "acceptanceCriteria": "Justification provided for choice of continuum elastoplastic constitutive model and frictional contact formulation relative to the physical phenomena of interest.",
      "rationale": "Bilinear isotropic hardening (Ti-6Al-4V, E=114 GPa, sigma_y=880 MPa) selected based on published material characterization. Augmented Lagrangian frictional contact (mu=0.2) captures screw-rod interface slip. Model form is consistent with prior published FDA FEA studies of ASTM F1717 constructs."
