      "rationale": "Ti-6Al-4V material properties sourced from ASTM F136 coupon test reports for the production lot. Screw and rod geometry digitized from CMM measurements of three representative specimens. Input uncertainty propagated via Latin hypercube sampling (n=200) to confirm QoI sensitivity."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test samples",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
