      "rationale": "N=11 non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs tested across two independent laboratories (Lab A: n=6, Lab B: n=5). All specimens from the same production lot; dimensional inspection confirmed ≤0.05 mm deviation from nominal. Inter-laboratory variability in stiffness was 3.2% CV."
    },
