      "rationale": "Construct stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement are the three QoIs specified in ASTM F1717 and directly inform the regulatory submission. Yield force is the primary indicator of structural integrity under worst-case surgical loading; all three QoIs are mechanistically linked to the fracture failure mode."
